uires the use of a t-J-like model, akin to that\nused in investigations of high T$_c$ superconductivity. The highly entangled\nstates discovered in the microscopic and model calculations of controllably\ndetuned, asymmetric, double wells suggest three-cold-atom DW quantum computing\nqubits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2016 02:17:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-30"}
